commits.message:
Merge branch 'devel'

Bugfix:
    - now forwarding stderr of remote workers to local stderr
    - tutorial.py actually exists now

Features:
    - class methods can be scheduled now if the class is Storable
    and decorated with @has_scheduled_methods.
    - NumpyData class, saves numpy data to binary file, passing filename
    by JSON.
    - Lambda class, stores a lambda function as a string to be
    evaluated, allowing bits of code to be moved around.

Extra:
    - Cosmology example (still needs to be expanded)
commits.author: jhidding
